description:
WILL WAHA AND KYRLANDE GET THEIR BODIES BACK?

Waha takes baths in the river! She no longer recognizes her own people, is afraid of everything… could this be a change in personality? Could she believe she is… human?

At the same time, Kyrlande, daughter of the Count of Nayelle, on a family cruise on the Pellucide, is also acting very strangely… As if she has lost all her manners. Logical, since the two personalities have been swapped!

A complete adventure in one book.
name: La Trolle impromptue

description: Batman was ready for Bane’s attack, but he’s not ready to face the identity of a young man killed while dressed as a super hero. When Lois & Chloe join the squad, things get even weirder. And Lex’s decision leads to an unprecedented event for Superman!

description: Tracy LeMaster, the previous Seeker is incarcerated in a mental institute in a special room with no chance of escape...or so it was thought. More about the legacy of Seeker is revealed but what is true and what is imagination?
